window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The race to find the most valuable resource in the galaxy is on.</p> <p>No, it isn’t unobtainium, vibranium, adamantium, or eternium. And it isn’t a zouchem crystal, either (though that would be a nice pickup).</p> <p>If Ben wants to prevent Duke Sedaya from gaining an iron grip on the Hegemony, his only hope lies in locating the missing Prince Hiro. Of course, it won’t be easy. And even if Ben can find him, it may already be too late.</p>"; 
